  "text": "The Ethics Committee at the Polish Mother's Memorial Hospital -Research Institute, Lodz, Poland (No. 64/2016) approved the protocol for each study. Parents of all the children qualified for the experiment gave written consent for participation of their children in the study. The Ethics Committee approved the protocol. [CITATION_1] , b goitre incidence (BSA-adjusted) according to the reference values proposed by Zimmermann et al. [CITATION_2] , c goitre incidence (age-adjusted) according to the reference values proposed by Szybiński et al. [CITATION_3] .",
